desc_short	-----								Inspired by Mario Galaxy, Yoshi's Island, and Ecco the Dolphin, Airscape is a fast-paced, ultra-challenging 60 level action platformer. You play a deep-sea octopus, kidnapped by a mechanical alien race. Jump, dodge, and swim through a skybound environment full of floating islands, water formations, and robotic terrors.							
developer									Cross-Product								
